==English==
===Etymology===
From ''Hellenistis'' (''Ελληνιστής'') a user of the Greek language.

===Noun Phrase===
# [[Koine]] the [[Greek]] language from the time of Alexander the Great (say 325 BC) until foundation of Constantinople (AD 330).

